text: EastIndo is a charter airline based in Jakarta, Indonesia. Eastindo is listed in category 2 by Indonesian Civil Aviation Authority for airline safety quality. ==History== ==Destinations== EastIndo Raytheon *Dumai - Pinang Kampai Airport *Jakarta - Halim Perdanakusuma Airport *Medan - Kualanamu International Airport *Pangkalan Kerinci - Sultan Syarief Haroen Setia Negara Airport *Pekanbaru - Sultan Syarif Kasim II International Airport *Singapore - Seletar Airport *Surabaya - Juanda International Airport ==Fleet== The EastIndo fleets includes the following aircraft (as of May 2017): EastIndo Islander at Sultan Syarif Kasim II International Airport. * 2 Beechcraft B1900D * 2 Britten-Norman Islander * 2 Airbus Helicopter AS350 ==References== ==External links== *Official website *EastIndo Fleet Category:Airlines of Indonesia
